  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate",
    "asOf": "2012-02-01",
    "date": "2012-03-09T18:19:28Z",
    "text": "Fair Military Leave Act - Directs the Secretary concerned to make a payment to each member of the Armed Forces who was eligible to participate in the Post-Deployment/Mobilization Respite Absence program, but did not participate for one or more days due to government error.\n\nMakes such payment: (1) $200 for each day of non-participation, and (2) in lieu of any authorized administrative absence for such day(s)."
  },
